{"tid":2172493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」雙冠王閻維文給江澤民同習近平戴咗綠帽","createTime":"2020-08-24T15:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T04:51:38.000Z","uid":313615,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"843ca1fe5fa2bcabbbdb39fd83dc76c06c3e1679","tid":2172493,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"彭麗媛女士有個男朋友閻維文，閻維文有個女朋友宋祖英，宋祖英有個男朋友江澤民，彭麗媛有個老公習近平。<br />\n<br />\n彭麗媛女士同男朋友閻維文有個女兒閻晶晶，閻晶晶同李肇星嘅仔李禾禾結婚，彭麗媛女士係閻晶晶同李禾禾嘅介紹人<br />\n<br />\n彭麗媛女士同男朋友閻維文喺房間里嘅事都畀監控咗；<br />\n<br />\n閻維文係現代版嘅溫太醫。"},{"pid":"abba31670e13a1c75b193784e738ba34c2d9fdcb","tid":2172493,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/9kpZFUGJb9A20eH/status/1297741834760855553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F9kpZFUGJb9A20eH%2Fstatus%2F1297741834760855553&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b007f3c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F9kpZFUGJb9A20eH%2Fstatus%2F1297741834760855553&h=b0d6d032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/9kpZFUGJb9A20eH/status/1297741834760855553</a>"},{"pid":"93521aed9d4b19946904333a49056633fef55b6a","tid":2172493,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odzsCPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodzsCPQ.jpg&h=76536c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cciw4uO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcciw4uO.jpg&h=5f48cdca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsvzhPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsvzhPP.jpg&h=12de9502&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3087d9220947e2b257f79541f19393e46b7e0acf","tid":2172493,"uid":95520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0